Reasoning: The paper deals with principles for models of computation and gives category-theoretic axioms for describing updates to finite objects. This suggests that the paper may belong to the Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses functors and their role in encoding computation, which could also place it in the Programming Languages (cs.PL) or Category Theory (cs.CC) sub-categories. The paper also deals with updating computations, which could place it in the Data Structures (cs.DS) or Information Theory (cs.IT) sub-categories.
